name: We Used To Live Around Here

metadata.name: We Used To Live Around Here I
metadata.description:
We Used To Leave Around Here
A collection of  Composite Photography 

1/1 7360 x 4912 Pixels

I am a storyteller using Photography and 3D to create staged images which are alternately playful, often mysterious, thought-provoking, and at times disturbing. 
I compose my models  into digital created sets where they become characters in  my  world. 

I consider my work to be voyeuristic. Exposing the women bodies and asking them to perform titillating scenarios. But the women on my images are always in control
